The,service,connects,the,behavioral,profile,for,a,user,account,to,email,marketing,and,CRM,functions,to,target,communications,based,on,customer,actions,It,syncs,records,of,customer,activities,with,back,end,systems,to,enable,delivery,of,timely,and,highly,relevant,communications,API,methods,support,tracking,and,profiling,of,users,based,on,their,online,behavior,with,activity,scoring,and,location,information,Methods,also,support,dynamic,content,generation,and,personalized,delivery,with,marketing,messaging,generated,to,synchronize,with,related,behaviors